Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:49.49,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理\N無標題
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.08,0:01:48.70,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.70,0:01:49.49,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,——真由氏☆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.65,0:04:18.60,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圓桌會議是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.69,0:06:15.79,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託\N我還是想借用\N一下IBN5100啊\N行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:16.15,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,021219343537\N買六合彩去\N絕對能中！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.50,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18}收信人：約翰·提托\N標題：有事情想問你\N那個程式代碼是SERN的資料庫\N我成功發明了能把簡訊\N發往過去的機器\N如果往過去發送簡訊\N過去被改變的話\N世界線會發生變化嗎？\N一部分事情成了\N「不存在的事情」\N還有什麼別的影響嗎？\N你說過世界是由\N多元世界說構成的\N那個根據…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:29.03,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳子\N標題：彩票\N真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.88,0:18:36.09,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs18}閃光的指壓師\N標題：真高興\N下次告訴我更多\N關於時間機器的事情吧\N一定哦！\N約好了！\N再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.18,0:19:48.49,mail,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰·提托\N真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.95,0:00:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顫抖吧  我的右手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照契約  聽我號令
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纏繞著黑色火焰  滿足我的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.46,0:00:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話沒辦法再熱炸雞了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.84,0:00:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的好嗎  要當實驗室成員的話就得和那種人打交道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:28.84,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理  這已經不再是微波爐了  是時間機器了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.94,0:00:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太野蠻了  那麼小岡倫買台新的微波爐回來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒那麼多錢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.92,0:00:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過禁止拍我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.08,0:00:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留作紀念…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之不要拍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  程式搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.01,0:00:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電話微波爐第二版ver  1.03完成
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣電話微波爐上的手機就能給想發的號碼發送D-Mail了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.73,0:00:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  阿至
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:00:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就再次開始實驗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…是時間機器？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.58,0:01:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要公開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.62,0:01:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是店長是不是又會生氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.18,0:01:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.56,0:01:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.24,0:01:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85\fscy85}嘟嘟嚕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.65,0:01:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理  安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:16.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr.布朗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.19,0:01:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.73,0:01:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我爸爸不是Mr.布朗…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.20,0:01:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長的話外出工作去了  暫時不會回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.39,0:01:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.18,0:01:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然我怎麼可能在這裡偷懶…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.29,0:01:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.24,0:01:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明多汁炸雞No.1的話更好吃的說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.19,0:03:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  沒買樂倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.19,0:03:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣光了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.31,0:03:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是賣光了你就應該去找  直至找到為止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.85,0:03:48.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是作為一個樂倍飯所應該做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.33,0:03:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有就是沒有沒辦法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.65,0:03:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:04:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪個世界會有擔心蔬菜攝取量不足的瘋狂科學家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  開圓桌會議吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是把窗戶打開吧  不熱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼  阿至
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.93,0:04:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被機關知道了我們的秘密怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想乙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在開始進入掌管過去的女神作戰第二階段
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(338,325)\fscy80\fscx80}Operation  Urd
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行讓D-Mail更加具有實用價值的實驗…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.77,0:04:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天就得喝大麥茶才對呢  萌郁小姐要喝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更有實用價值的話要做什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.52,0:04:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改變過去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.63,0:04:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  那也太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是發生時間悖論的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,助手啊  你作為一個科學家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:53.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道就不想試一試能不能用D-Mail改變過去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要改變什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問得好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要通過本次作戰來達成的目的  那就是——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,買彩票中獎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.48,0:05:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫…真由氏表示悲哀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我贊成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有錢的話就能買PC的新組件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:17.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且還可以隨便去MayQueen那裡玩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來  我覺得應該考慮怎樣讓世界變得更加和平之類的才對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.70,0:05:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說讓世界上每個人都擁有一個嗚帕靠枕什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部  你的志向也太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.70,0:05:31.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是確認過去到底能不能改變的實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.03,0:05:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是最能夠顯示出結果的方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是目的不是錢嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.68,0:05:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  Celeb17
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ce…Cele…  啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Celeb  17
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.50,0:05:46.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個花父母的錢住賓館的人沒資格說我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經18歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.40,0:05:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  彩票不是有很多種嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.39,0:05:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要買哪種的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.72,0:05:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.13,0:05:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  一點都不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…你沒回信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這難道說就是所謂的「{\1c&0000E0&}sweets（笑）{\r}」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克里斯汀娜  認真看好她別讓她隨意到處亂跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.11,0:06:26.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…就算你讓我看好她也…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萌郁小姐想看看這間實驗室嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.67,0:06:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼過一會我會帶你看的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.68,0:06:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是真由氏擅長做的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也帶紅莉栖看過的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先從哪裡開始呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  買六合彩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每週四公佈中獎號碼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把那個發回過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的要幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有其他更好的提議嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:06:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要選擇哪個號碼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便說一下  一等獎…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.66,0:07:03.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…兩億？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩…兩億？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  阿至
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:08.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩億有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.62,0:07:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一等獎還是太招人耳目了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我還是被機關所追蹤的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:14.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你退縮了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二…二等呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.79,0:07:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…兩千三百萬元
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.53,0:07:21.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七十萬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.48,0:07:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就那個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部還真是膽小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:29.38,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是擔心發生時間悖論啊你有意見嗎Cel-7
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:30.90,up,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要略成Cel-7啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.89,0:07:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這就是嗚帕靠枕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.36,0:07:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累的時候或者是沒精神的時候  就可以抱一抱它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有  這個是冰箱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天裡面有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.38,0:07:40.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  閃光的指壓師
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.70,0:07:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給你作為實驗室成員的第一個任務吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:07:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是第一件工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.82,0:08:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思考怎樣組織D-Mail的簡訊內容
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.79,0:08:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓一週前什麼也不知道的我  去買六合彩的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.24,0:08:12.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七天前的話  也就是168小時…定170秒左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:16.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  差不多這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.98,0:08:21.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到了打開命運石之門的時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.74,0:08:24.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了？  真是不會膩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.41,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是  不要每次都來潑冷水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.70,0:08:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為看你們…很開心的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒…沒什麼好開心的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.54,0:08:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說回來  這位助手還真是一位傲嬌小姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.19,0:08:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰是傲嬌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.79,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  牧瀨氏懂什麼是傲嬌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你那是知道的反應吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不知道就是不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.48,0:08:54.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我就啟動微波爐了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.42,0:09:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是發生時間悖論的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.58,0:09:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我在擔心什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,EL  PSY  CONGROO！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.47,0:09:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.85,0:09:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.97,0:09:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.92,0:10:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛…剛才是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在這裡站了多久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.15,0:10:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概30秒左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.61,0:10:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30秒？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不記得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才你不是說要進行用D-Mail改變過去的實驗嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:25.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就來到電話微波爐的跟前然後就「哈…哈…」地呻吟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏  剛才那句「哈…哈…」的再說…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.23,0:10:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  變態
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.39,0:10:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.43,0:10:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.82,0:10:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部  你真的沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.20,0:10:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢呢？  六合彩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.58,0:10:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cel-7  我中了三等獎了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.93,0:10:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要叫我Cel-7…  你在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:10:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼…  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:04.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是實驗  我們做實驗驗證是否能夠用D-Mail改變過去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說大家現在正在討論用什麼樣的內容比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.37,0:11:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由氏覺得應該思考怎樣讓世界變得更加和平之類的比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.14,0:11:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說讓世界上每個人都擁有一個嗚帕靠枕什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx85\fscy85}真的…不記得了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.96,0:11:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.24,0:11:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳  歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.11,0:11:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真師傅  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.85,0:11:41.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,02  12  18…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.96,0:11:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉佳子  你在哪裡知道這個的？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.23,0:11:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…  凶真師傅告訴我這個號碼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.20,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.20,0:11:54.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說可能會中獎  去買買看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.35,0:11:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.37,0:11:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一週前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.45,0:12:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫有預知能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼琉佳氏  你中了獎了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.50,0:12:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  我搞錯了一個號碼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可惜  太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部  你難道用電話微波爐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.39,0:12:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒買樂倍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.95,0:12:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有就是沒有沒辦法的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.86,0:12:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實應該發送了D-Mail
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.85,0:12:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻沒有發信記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.34,0:12:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為過去被改寫了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.66,0:12:47.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們記不得實驗的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.89,0:12:51.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明一起商量  一起看著的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.73,0:12:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我還記得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.94,0:13:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種感覺和那時候一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.50,0:13:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.28,0:13:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:17.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.72,0:13:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.97,0:13:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉好像被洗腦了的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.78,0:13:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗腦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.46,0:13:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被洗腦了的究竟是我  還是他們…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.93,0:13:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有被植入晶片
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:56.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  沒有被洗腦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:13:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晶…晶片？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「洗腦」是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.56,0:14:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我鳳凰院凶真來告訴你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綯好像害怕岡部倫太郎啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想問你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.93,0:14:22.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放電？  是指那個搖搖晃晃的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.57,0:14:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才有過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.39,0:14:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,10分鐘左右前也應該有過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.53,0:14:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那次沒注意到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:30.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.70,0:14:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個變態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.60,0:14:36.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不是變態呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.83,0:14:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是「變態紳士」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  我說過可以聽到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.30,0:14:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到聽得這麼清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.74,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說你  連時間機器的事情也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真行啊  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忠告你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  對誰都不會說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.60,0:14:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說在煩惱著時間機器的事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  問問約翰·提托如何
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.36,0:15:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來提托曾經說過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.14,0:15:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往過去  並改變過去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(260,325)\fscy80\fscx80}divergence
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.11,0:15:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名為世界線變動率的數值會產生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.01,0:15:15.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界會移動向另一條世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在移動時
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.03,0:15:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變化前的世界線的記憶會被消除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.35,0:15:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在新世界線的記憶會被重新構造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.63,0:15:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過D-Mail  從琉佳子沒買六合彩的世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,移動到了買了的世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.05,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界線發生變化
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去的流向也發生了改變
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.02,0:15:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是沒有把能中六合彩的D-Mail發往過去的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.56,0:15:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是真由理他們不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.69,0:15:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是世界本身就不存在實驗這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.33,0:15:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼為何  只有我擁有那個記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.93,0:16:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.17,0:16:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綯  不管被問什麼也不能說我偷懶了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次能帶我坐自行車嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.44,0:16:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶你坐帶你坐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部倫太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.08,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會幫你加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.86,0:16:21.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.45,0:16:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部  你對我女兒做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我什麼也沒…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.16,0:16:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴  和我可愛的女兒兩人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像你這樣的傢伙怎麼可能抑制得住慾望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎麼看別人的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先根本就不是兩人獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.74,0:16:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到剛才為止鈴羽還在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.81,0:16:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎  綯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為說好了  所以不能說她偷懶了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.62,0:16:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.15,0:16:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  打工的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝天謝地謝天謝地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.83,0:16:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  偷懶了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.38,0:16:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,42吋電視怎麼一直開著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.85,0:17:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.53,0:17:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因之後解釋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的實驗暫時中止
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家就地解散吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那邊的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.37,0:17:30.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.31,0:17:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微考慮點事情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:34.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.72,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回了賓館也是寂寞的一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.00,0:17:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望我搭理你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.15,0:17:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子Cel-7
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了別叫Cel-7
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.78,0:17:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要忙著發簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.15,0:17:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都想待在這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:49.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就別礙事  放安靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,325)\fscy80\fscx80\fsp0}The Zombie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復活者
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.37,0:17:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個叫法最讓人生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,簡直就像戀愛中的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.70,0:18:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等喜歡的人發來簡訊一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.03,0:18:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就那麼希望我搭理你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發簡訊的對象是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰·提托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.70,0:18:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿至？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.03,0:18:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.16,0:18:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我發現了一個不得了的失誤
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失誤？  是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.39,0:18:55.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.48,0:18:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把錢包忘在研究所了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:18:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.27,0:19:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果進不去MayQueen
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.97,0:19:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小岡倫  幫…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.99,0:19:08.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘟嘟嚕  小岡倫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.35,0:19:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  是真由理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.54,0:19:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿至也在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.46,0:19:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要借錢給他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.95,0:19:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是小岡倫  打起精神了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.79,0:19:21.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果還沒的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱抱真由氏的嗚帕也可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就能打起精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.42,0:19:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我要掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打工好好加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.42,0:19:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.03,0:19:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部  笑容滿面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.85,0:19:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了你的簡訊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同你的推測
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.02,0:19:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無疑問過去改變  世界線進行了移動
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.93,0:20:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯一不明的地方是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.99,0:20:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還擁有著改變之前的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是事實嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.23,0:20:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.70,0:20:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前也發生過同樣的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.15,0:20:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:17.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過簡訊來改變過去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.62,0:20:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我所在的2036年也是未曾預想過的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.37,0:20:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這次改變了過去  移動了世界線
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.26,0:20:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是越過世界線仍保持記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:33.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能觀測到變動的人類
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.24,0:20:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今都未曾確認過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.24,0:20:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…凶真
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你或許擁有那種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:46.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是你的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.94,0:20:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許可以引導世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.14,0:20:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往世界線變動率1%的另一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導世界？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界線變動率1%的另一邊是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.59,0:21:04.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡究竟有著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那前方有著真正的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不越過那堵牆壁的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.48,0:21:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來就會成為反烏托邦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.57,0:21:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目的是改變未來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且擁有那力量的或許是你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:41.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部…怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.99,0:21:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我將未來…這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.41,0:22:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凶真  希望你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.34,0:22:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能成為救世主


